            <div class="text">
                <h2>DNS手動修改</h2>
                <p>请试试下方的步骤，为您排解问题</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ben_menu">
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_B.html">windows XP</a>
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_A.html">windows 7</a>
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_C.html" style="background-color:#0E0E0E; color:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #FFF;">windows 8.1</a>
                <a href="ClearDNS_File_D.html">windows 10</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="CearCachel">
            <div class="Text_A1" style="top: 175px;">开启 "<strong>设置</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A2" style="top: 625px;">选择 "<strong>控制面板</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A3" style="top: 1065px;">选择 "<strong>网络和共享中心</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A4" style="top: 1410px;">点击 "<strong>本地连接</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A5" style="top: 1755px;">开启本地连接的介面后
                <br />点击 "<strong>属性(P)</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A6" style="top: 2100px;">开启属性(P)的介面后
                <br />勾选 "<strong>Internet 协议版本 4 (TCP/IPv4)</strong>"
                <br />点击 "<strong>属性(R)</strong>"</div>
            <div class="Text_A7" style="top: 2815px;">开启属性(R)的介面后
                <br />选择 "<strong>使用下面的 DNS 服务器地址(E)</strong>"，
                <br />并修改:
                <br/>首选DNS服务器(P): <strong>8 . 8 . 8 . 8</strong>
                <br /> 备用DNS服务器(A): <strong>8 . 8 . 4 . 4</strong>
                <br />点击 "<strong>确定</strong>"即完成DNS设置。</div>
